    "body": "### Problem\n\nI don't use tabs ever in my setup. When I check an help page it opens a window. Everything either opens a new window or a new floating window. Currently `:checkhealth` seems to be the only place that opens tabs\n\n### Expected behavior\n\nOpening in a new window or at least give an option to specify how it should open.",
